text: Urban is an unincorporated community in Skagit County, in the U.S. state of Washington. ==History== A post office called Urban was established in 1895, and remained in operation until 1971. The community was named after Urban Stenger. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Skagit County, Washington Category:Unincorporated communities in Washington (state)
title: Urban, Washington
